column2: Hover over the event option for my levy efficiency law. If no tooltip appears, I have no dynlevy law applied.

Dynamic Levy Law: §Ydynlevy_0§!
Levy Efficiency: §Y100%§!
Realm Size: §Y1§! through §Y19§!
As the size of a decentralized feudal realm grows, its efficiency at raising liege levies drops. Demesne levies are unaffected.\n\nRealm size range: §Y1§!-§Y19§!
